description: Opportunity to own a large single family with a desirable East Side location. Brimming with potential, boasting 2,554 sq ft of space, this residence is ready to transform into your dream home! The existing first floor has tall ceilings, living room, formal dining room, kitchen and access to private outdoor space. The second level has 2 bedrooms, office, and full bathroom. Top floor has 2 large bedrooms. Finished basement with full bathroom. This property is also being offered as a ZBA approved 2 family, ask listing agent for more details.
